reviewText: I ordered a DVD...I got a CD

Yes, It is not very long, but it's an awesome video. The audio sounds great to me so I'm not sure about some of the other reviews.
Normally, I think most live performances are not quiet as good as studio versions, but this one is top notch, put it in, crank it up loud and enjoy!
It didn't have any indestructable songs on it. Im a tad confused on y its called indestructable. Gave it away.

If you are a Disturbed Fan you will love this. They sound amazing live. I have found some really decent boot leg live stuff by them but this completes it all for now. I am sure they will have many greatest hits CD in the future.

Give us more!!! They are strong live, I just wish it had more tunes on it. Cool response from the crowd interacting with the band and strong showing of how good they are live. Again, just wish there was more...

I found this at a dollar store and thought i'd give it a try. Glad i didn't pay much for it,the video quality is ok but what hurts it is the very poor audio,sounds horrible. Six songs total,no wonder best buy had a bunch of these that never sold. If you can get it cheap it might be worth it to you,otherwise it's not worth more than about 4 dollars.

This is a short Ditrurbed concert video made in Germany. It has some new and some old music on it - 5 songs total I think. The camera work is good but the sound quality doesn't hold up well on my surround system and that's my biggest complaint with it - sounds sort of flat. I bought this used to watch while I ride my stationary bike and didn't pay that much for it so I got my moneys worth.
